{"tid":1743878,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［長文］選舉近了，提防散水黨","createTime":"2019-11-21T12:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T12:21:35.000Z","uid":208943,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4aba51886437014f634d0620035a7d7778c8344e","tid":1743878,"uid":208943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"睇文前想大家諗諗<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">區選有咩用</span></span>？區選對於落實真雙普選<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有咩幫助</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n所謂民主係指<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主權在民</span></span>，而往往要達致民主都係得兩種方式，分別係政府帶頭喺<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">制度內改革</span></span>同由民眾帶頭喺<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">制度外革命</span></span>。但係，喺《基本法》入面寫明香港特別行政區既主權<span style=\"color: red;\">屬於</span>中華人民共和國。即係話，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97以嚟從來都冇民主</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n既然一直以嚟都係假民主咁點解仲要參與假選舉。假選舉根本就冇任何認受性。今時今日，既然決心要透過抗爭嚟爭取民主，否定現時政府既<span style=\"color: red;\">正當性</span>，點解仲要參與呢場政制底下既選舉，呢個行為等同於承認政府既正當性。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你覺得假選舉係可以接受，咁點解你唔接受人大831</span></span>？更何況而家仲要有DQ。<br />\n<br />\n然後就係，區議會係一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">諮詢機構</span></span>，佢既作用分分鐘仲廢過監警會。對於現時既抗爭運動又有咩用？<br />\n<br />\n至於今屆區選係<span style=\"color: red;\">變相公投論</span>，所以要區選。咁以前嗰幾屆嘅區議會同立法會選舉唔通唔係公投咩？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想知道民意點解唔睇民調</span></span>？仲有立法會直選反對派次次都過半㗎啦咁代表唔到民意咩？仲有呢個政府係驚民意嘅話二百萬加一就跪咗啦，又唔見共產黨驚到瀨屎？議會制失效係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為有功能組別啊嘛</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n之後就係因為資源所以要議席論。冇錯議席的確可以拎到資源。不過，我哋手足出嚟流血流汗甚至被自殺被強姦唔係為咗幫你拉票，麻煩對俾返小小尊重我哋，唔好成日拎任何抗爭運動入面嘅事件嚟拉票eg周同學。仲有人哋建制派資源無限有共產黨俾，所以根本斷唔到佢哋米路。<br />\n<br />\n結論就係，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">制度唔變咩都係假</span></span>。呢樣同樣都適用黑警。<br />\n<br />\n即使今日政府解散三萬黑警，聽日佢都可以換一批新嘅三萬黑警上嚟打死你。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日共產黨拎住把刀嚟斬你，你點會只係拎走佢把刀？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然區選冇用麻煩大家之後繼續抗爭，唔好以為投完票就當贏。<br />\n<br />\n覺得我係鬼嘅麻煩起咗我底先，就算我係鬼唔代表我講嘅嘢唔可以係合理。"},{"pid":"cd7f3f5d78591e4a9ef252ac62a9b60b89818f61","tid":1743878,"uid":208943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:05:50.000Z","msg":"對於某啲政黨同議員，我本小數薄好厚"},{"pid":"73dcbb82bcd347b1625abad12e7264d2f75efdff","tid":1743878,"uid":208943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:06:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fee8aec9e01f06780b6d8402753c4382b7f28694","tid":1743878,"uid":208943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd55b59e0b06bb6b17b3c0446b18adcbc750bfed","tid":1743878,"uid":208943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07da21d23e6b9fb1232aefe1b0b5e37b556ae523","tid":1743878,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:07:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗爭時不分和勇<br />\n投票時不分和勇</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落啊，<br />\n和理非星期日需要你"},{"pid":"312dbce8c91d3c2d986fe19a8b544b6f833c401d","tid":1743878,"uid":208943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"我冇話唔投<br />\n都冇話叫人唔好投"},{"pid":"662334360c83695ba249ebda500a99eef5676876","tid":1743878,"uid":208943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d37f4548ef9a8fe820a850c1b428824ee492091","tid":1743878,"uid":208943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91fd8133167eee6fba11dd5782a24604c1f0ae2","tid":1743878,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f639f24e5766ef0c8ed208607e09db5bace1e504","tid":1743878,"uid":208943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}